{"tid":2203612,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方: 同意新屋嶺不適合於大型公眾活動中用作羈押被捕者 今年6月底起已停用","createTime":"2020-09-15T12:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T12:56:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7696992c34f52b6e821dd7d0bdbb42086d160a3a","tid":2203612,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:44:30.000Z","msg":"監警會今午舉行例行會議，警方投訴警察課代表在會上匯報3項已完成建議。警方指，就監警會第52項建議，目前已完成檢視臨時羈留處的選址，並確定由5個陸路總區、各指定2間警署，用作羈留大型公眾活動中的被捕者。<br />\n<br />\n警方舉例指，選址包括紅磡警署及秀茂坪警署，因其位置交通便利、附近有公立醫院，故已選為西九龍及東九龍總區的指定臨時羈留處，並於9月6日公眾活動中用作處理被捕者。<br />\n<br />\n此外，警方亦同意新屋嶺扣留中心目前的條件，不適合於大型公眾活動中用作羈押被捕者，並今年6月底起已停用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/GLWWKZ5SIRBRDMFXSDLTP6GNAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FGLWWKZ5SIRBRDMFXSDLTP6GNAM%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIudLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=b75a37be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FGLWWKZ5SIRBRDMFXSDLTP6GNAM%2F&h=8be482be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/GLWWKZ5SIRBRDMFXSDLTP6GNAM/</a>"},{"pid":"e01ac19066bb3fd6363dd700251bd083918b91b0","tid":2203612,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65d4dacdae62533a38a02f12ce3a36254595531","tid":2203612,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e01ac19066bb3fd6363dd700251bd083918b91b0","tid":2203612,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class